        "where_headed": {
          "type": "content_block",
          "settings": {
            "label": "Where we are headed",
            "heading": "Still early. Deliberately so.",
            "text": "<p>In 2025, we are expanding into personal wellness and smart home — with the same rigour we brought to audio and personal care. We are building same-day delivery coverage across India's top twelve cities. The catalogue will grow, but the standard will not move.</p><p>If you have found something here that surprised you, that is the point. And if you believe a product belongs on Blissway, write to us at <a href=\"mailto:care@blissway.online\">care@blissway.online</a> — we read every message.</p>"
          }
